import React, { Component } from "react";
import "./form.css"
import {Row, Col} from "antd"

export default class UserForm extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
        <>
        <Row>
        <Col xs={{ span: 5, offset: 1 }} lg={{ span: 6, offset: 2 }}>
          Col
        </Col>
        <Col xs={{ span: 11, offset: 1 }} lg={{ span: 6, offset: 2 }}>
          Col
        </Col>
        <Col xs={{ span: 5, offset: 1 }} lg={{ span: 6, offset: 2 }}>
          Col
        </Col>
      </Row>
        <Row>
        <Col xs={{ span: 5, offset: 1 }} lg={{ span: 6, offset: 2 }}>
          Col
        </Col>
        <Col xs={{ span: 11, offset: 1 }} lg={{ span: 6, offset: 2 }}>
          Col
        </Col>
        <Col xs={{ span: 5, offset: 1 }} lg={{ span: 6, offset: 2 }}>
          Col
        </Col>
      </Row>
        <Row>
        <Col xs={{ span: 5, offset: 1 }} lg={{ span: 6, offset: 2 }}>
          Col
        </Col>
        <Col xs={{ span: 11, offset: 1 }} lg={{ span: 6, offset: 2 }}>
          Col
        </Col>
        <Col xs={{ span: 5, offset: 1 }} lg={{ span: 6, offset: 2 }}>
          Col
        </Col>
      </Row>
      </>
    );
  }
}
